data.description:
Premium Oversized GOLF COURSE LOT with Lake View!!  This Spacious Home offers a Beautiful Primary Suite and a SECOND 1st Floor Bedroom and Bath!!!!

OWNED, PAID SOLAR, Updated Oven, Microwave and Dishwasher, NEW ROOF, New Garage Door Opener in 2023, New Inverter on Solar, 3 HVAC Zones.

3 morel bedrooms & 3rd bath, can be used for offices, or hobbies as well as added private Guest space.  The Home is great for entertaining or quiet enjoyment!  Whole-house Vacuum, Intercom System, Surround Sound, Upgraded Cherry Cabinets, Stone Countertops, Gas hookup for cooktop & clothes dryer,  Pull-out Shelves in cabinets, Dog Run, Park-like backyard with Water Feature, Covered Patio, Gas Fire Pit, and BBQ Island are ideal for Arizona Living.          ELIGIBLE for Low Interest VA Loan Assumption! Please NOTE:  There are blinds and sunscreens in the garage
